{"tid":1897630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利疫情擴散增至11人死亡　歐盟稱暫不考慮封關，可能因為死得太少人了","createTime":"2020-02-25T22:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T01:36:10.000Z","uid":125193,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a08c86353181b1054500bcf85b7f5db47f02fd","tid":1897630,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:39:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510802-20200226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510802-20200226.htm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=17c9ef62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510802-20200226.htm&h=b2e65951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510802-20200226.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎在歐洲擴散，意大利增至11人死亡，超過320宗確診，個案由北部蔓延至南部西西里島。總理孔特強調當地的防控措施有效，仍然是安全的旅遊目的地。<br />\n<br />\n意大利的鄰國瑞士、奧地利及克羅地亞先後出現首宗確診病例，全部患者都與意大利有關，不過，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歐盟表示，暫時未有成員國考慮對意大利封關。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n伊朗的死亡個案增至15人，確診者包括負責抗疫最高級的衛生部副部長。巴林增至23宗確診，科威特、伊拉克及阿曼都有確診，全部新增患者都去過伊朗。"},{"pid":"e40249dd88c66e50da159fb9704961e60d54ebb3","tid":1897630,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe382d443360a99dfb6098a971a096763ef1bc96","tid":1897630,"uid":17313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:53:52.000Z","msg":"On9 等攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788ddc941586cbbb03bf9d9e5010af54a0559649","tid":1897630,"uid":54824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T22:55:07.000Z","msg":"越來越多perfect storms"},{"pid":"e1